{"tid":1557262,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(RTHK) 據了解休班警員獲發伸縮警棍　休班期間執行警察職務","createTime":"2019-09-10T04:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T05:21:35.000Z","uid":66324,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"792c72f63038ca8da17d4cd6b6071533810b3e8c","tid":1557262,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:46:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479800-20190910.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479800-20190910.htm&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdDw5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=e66737ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479800-20190910.htm&h=5812dd8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479800-20190910.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n據了解，警方同意向休班警員發放伸縮警棍，讓他們在休班期間執行警察職務，預計警方今日下午起會開始派發，一個月後檢討。<br />\n<br />\n本台接獲文件，指有關伸縮警棍會有特別標記，行動部會根據各主要單位的實額人數分發警棍。<br />\n<br />\n文件表示，無論警員是否當值期間使用警棍，都會被視作使用武力，亦要遵照相關警察通例，強調警員與市民接觸時，必須自律和高度克制，除非有絕對需要，而且無其他辦法可完成合法任務，否則不得使用武力。警員使用警棍前要表明身分，並在情況許可下盡量向對方發警告，說明將使用警棍。"},{"pid":"79cd6b2c26e441e19453ae68fea9078b6183d403","tid":1557262,"uid":61678,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:48:12.000Z","msg":"指引呢d野又唔係法律 差佬駛鬼理"},{"pid":"48e6069a2c1c06c4e6f372793fed1cab8696655a","tid":1557262,"uid":276393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:50:14.000Z","msg":"以為警槍 咁巴閉"},{"pid":"7fe102e97de8aab709bc3188f386a66c5bdb2df4","tid":1557262,"uid":184801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:52:17.000Z","msg":"7x24行街隨時俾人扑<br />\n告埋非法集結<br />\n入新屋嶺集中營"},{"pid":"a303c3371dbeb8e80eb468f8dd3180c4de6aa39f","tid":1557262,"uid":211565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:59:36.000Z","msg":"執行警察職務 姐係老笠 食霸王雞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7fa7329678e21e9338e6fdf3b0bb08c30d6b055","tid":1557262,"uid":240682,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T05:16:17.000Z","msg":"好似睇到有單爆格10條友搶左兩球幾，當中都係有人拎伸縮警棍 係咪有咩暗示"},{"pid":"904c9b98c463aec4dcec6382963f9ddd283b2039","tid":1557262,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T05:21:35.000Z","msg":"推上國際"}]}